{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcbd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5532"},"text":"§ 5532.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Hypersonic defense capability development","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcbe-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Agent","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Director of the Missile Defense Agency shall serve as the executive agent for the Department of Defense for the development of a capability by the United States to counter hypersonic boost-glide vehicle capabilities and conventional prompt strike capabilities that may be employed against the United States, the allies of the United States, and the deployed forces of the United States.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcbf-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Duties","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In carrying out subsection (a), the Director shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcc0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" develop architectures for a hypersonic defense capability, from detecting threats to intercepting such threats, that—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcc1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" involves systems of the military departments and the Defense Agencies; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcc2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" includes both kinetic and nonkinetic options for such interception; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcc3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5532/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" not later than ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 2017","children":[],"tail":", establish a program of record to develop a hypersonic defense capability."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaab5fcc4-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/159/dA/tXVI/s1649/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVI, § 1649(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2024-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2024","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/138/2194"},"text":"138 Stat. 2194","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaab5fcc5-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaab5fcc6-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idaab5fcc7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 5532, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041"},"text":"act Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70A/318"},"text":"70A Stat. 318","children":[],"tail":", set forth classes of persons prohibited from enlisting in the naval service, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/235/s2/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–235, § 2(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", (b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-01-02"},"text":"Jan. 2, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/81/756"},"text":"81 Stat. 756","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Provisions similar to those in this section were contained in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/328/dA/tXVI/s1687"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–328, div. A, title XVI, § 1687","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/2629"},"text":"130 Stat. 2629","children":[],"tail":", which was set out in a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4205"},"text":"section 4205 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/159/dA/tXVI/s1649/b/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVI, § 1649(b)(5)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2024-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2024","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/138/2199"},"text":"138 Stat. 2199","children":